version_description: We've added the ability to "painnt" videos on your device, as well as create your own custom style by choosing any image you like and turning it into a filter. Awesome, right?!
We've added the ability to "painnt" videos on your device, as well as create your own custom style by choosing any image you like and turning it into a filter. Awesome, right?!

UPDATE NOTICE: If your effects don't work please delete the Cache (Tap on Menu, then on Cache, then tap on All) so that the new faster models are updated.

* The times are a'changin! We made Painnt much, much, really much faster! And also less memory hungry :)
* Introducing Time lapse videos: Render a video of your art coming alive! free of charge, mind you.
* We got rid of some bugs, bye bye bugs, you're not welcome.

Happy painnting y'all!

Painnt isn't a silly, no-brainer duh app, ok? This is a Pro app, a tool to perfect and tune your photos just the way you want them . So we packed in (even more) advanced features like variable brushes, precise output options of any ratio & size, and even the chance to draw & retouch images before processing.  Happy painnting!
